Name: DUTY
Explanation: AN ALPHANUMERIC CODE REPRESENTING A TACTICAL DUTY ASSIGNED TO A UNIT, COMMANDER OR COORDINATOR.

Name: LINK DUTY
Explanation: AN ALPHANUMERIC CODE FROM ATP 1(C) VOL II 3415 TABLE D REPRESENTING A DUTY UNDERTAKEN IN TACTICAL DATA LINK OPERATIONS.

Name: MULTILINK COORDINATION DUTY
Explanation: AN ACRONYM REPRESENTING A SPECIFIC COORDINATION DUTY REQUIRED IN MULTIPLE TACTICAL DATA LINK OPERATIONS.

Name: AIR COMMAND AND CONTROL DUTY ASSIGNED
Explanation: A TACTICAL AIR COMMAND AND CONTROL DUTY ASSIGNED TO A GROUND OR AIRBORNE UNIT TO ENSURE COHESIVE AND COORDINATED COMMAND AND CONTROL OF AIR OPERATIONS. RELATED DOCUMENT: CONCEPTS OF OPERATIONS FOR AIR OPS HEADQUARTERS AND UNITS.

Name: DUTY, OTHER
Explanation: A SHORT EXPLANATION OF A TACTICAL DUTY ASSIGNED TO EITHER A UNIT OR AN ORGANIZATION, THAT IS NOT CONTAINED IN ATP1 VOL2 CH34 TABLE D.

Name: CONTROL POSITION TYPE
Explanation: TYPE OF ASSET CONTROLLED BY A PARTICULAR CONTROL POSITION FUNCTION.

Name: DUTY NUMBER UNASSIGNED
Explanation: A NUMERIC CODE FOR A TACTICAL DUTY THAT IS NOT CONTAINED IN ATP1 VOL2 CH34 TABLE D.
